function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	Hydra.ActorSetConversationStatus(ACTOR_LORATH, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetConversationStatus(ACTOR_TAISSA, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetConversationStatus(ACTOR_NEYRELLE, false)
	
	Hydra.Wait(0.75)

	Hydra.QActorWait(ACTOR_LORATH, 0.75)

	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(ACTOR_LORATH, 1)
	
	Hydra.QActorWait(ACTOR_TAISSA, 0.25)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ACTOR_TAISSA, LOC_TAISSAENTER, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(ACTOR_TAISSA, 1)
	
	Hydra.QActorWait(ACTOR_NEYRELLE, 0.45)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ACTOR_NEYRELLE, LOC_NEYRELLEENTER, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(ACTOR_NEYRELLE, 1)
	
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONV_BARK, ACTOR_LORATH)
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(CONV_BARK)
	
	-- Add optional conversations
	Hydra.ActorSetConversationList(ACTOR_LORATH, CONVLIST_LORATH)
	Hydra.ActorSetConversationList(ACTOR_NEYRELLE, CONVLIST_NEYRELLE)
	Hydra.ActorSetConversationList(ACTOR_TAISSA, CONVLIST_TAISSA)
	
end

function Start(idActor, flPrevHP, flHp)

	-- First Time Reward Proxy Drop
	idFirstTimeRewardLocation = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(sFirstTimeRewardDropActor, idActor)
	
	tPlayers = Hydra.PlayerActorsInLevelArea(S_LEVELAREA_BOSS_ARENA)
	
	for i, Player in ipairs(tPlayers) do
	
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(CONV_HED_RTC, Player)
	
	end

	idElias = idActor
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idElias, "Elias_Boss_Death_Kill_All_Demons")
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idElias)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idTaissa)
	
	-- mark boss encounter as completed
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyComplete(S_LEVELAREA_BOSS_ARENA)
	
	--Remove the fogwall so player can advance to the next area
	local idFogWall = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("CSD_ZakFortCrypts_BossRoom_FogWallExitBlocker")[1]
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idFogWall)
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	------------------------------------------------------
	-- First Time Rewards

	local tAllPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
	
	for i, idPlayer in ipairs(tAllPlayers) do
		-- Drop the TreasureClass, which contains both "always" and "first time" rewards
		-- The First Time stuff is conditioned by the flag that is set after the drorp occurs
		-- idFirstTimeRewardLocation is set/created on "Actor Killed)
		Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActorForPlayer(idFirstTimeRewardLocation, "FirstTimeReward_Campaign_EliasHawezar", idPlayer)
		
		-- Set the variable, to mark that this player has recieved a reward
		Hydra.SetPlayerVariableFlag(idPlayer, "FirstTimeReward_Campaign_EliasHawezar")
	end
	
	-- Since this boss doesn't have its own treasure class, also drop generic treasure at this time
	Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActor(idFirstTimeRewardLocation, "Campaign_Boss")
	
	-- Remove the Reward Actor
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idFirstTimeRewardLocation)
	------------------------------------------------------
end

function Start()
	--enable boss encounter, so the fog wall is up
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyQueueStart(S_LEVELAREA_BOSS_ARENA)
	
	--Play Boss Music
	Hydra.MusicOverride("CSD_Hawe_Wetland_ZakFortCrypts", "Music_Boss_Elias_Phase1")
	
	if bRepeatBossFight == false then
		-- This removes the flagging done for theatre in the previous phase.
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idElias)
		Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idElias, true)
		Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idElias, false)
		bRepeatBossFight = true
		
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idTaissa) then
			Hydra.ActorAddAITarget(idTaissa, idElias, true)
		end
	else
		-- Turn the spawner back on
		idEliasSpawner = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("CSD_Hawe_Wetland_ZakFortCrypts_BossEncounterSpawners")[1]
		Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idEliasSpawner, false)
	end
	

end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)
	-- grab the Elias ID
	idElias = idActorSpawned
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idTaissa) then
		Hydra.ActorAddAITarget(idTaissa, idElias, true)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	-- Turn the spawner back on
	idEliasSpawner = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("CSD_Hawe_Wetland_ZakFortCrypts_BossEncounterSpawners")[1]
	Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idEliasSpawner, false)

end

function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)

	-- Get NPCs (and a Gate, Trigger and Ritual FX)
	idTaissa = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_TaissaTomb")[1]
	idDonan = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_DonanTomb")[1]
	idLorath = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_LorathTomb")[1]
	idNeyrelle = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_NeyrelleTomb")[1]
	idGate = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_TombGate")[1]
	idBossStartTrigger = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_BossStartTrigger")[1]
	idRitualFX = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_RitualFX")[1]
	
	-- Make NPCs visible
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idTaissa)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idDonan)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idLorath)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idNeyrelle)
	
	-- Get locations for NPCs to run to
	idDonanLoc = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_DonanTombLoc")[1]
	idLorathLoc = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_LorathTombLoc")[1]

	idTaissaLoc3 = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_TaissaTombLoc3")[1]

	--Hydra.TraceScreen("@@@@@@ idLorath is: ",idLorath)
	--Hydra.TraceScreen("@@@@@@ idLorathLoc is: ",idLorathLoc)
	
	Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONV_TAISSASENSE, idTaissa)
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(CONV_TAISSASENSE)

	
	-- Move everyone to location
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idDonan, idDonanLoc, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idDonan, idDonanLoc)
	
	Hydra.QActorWait(idLorath, 0.75)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idLorath, idLorathLoc, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idLorath, idLorathLoc)
	
	Hydra.QActorWait(idTaissa, 0.15)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idTaissa, idTaissaLoc, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idTaissa, idTaissaLoc)
	
	Hydra.QActorWait(idNeyrelle, 0.45)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idNeyrelle, idNeyrelleLoc, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idNeyrelle, idNeyrelleLoc)
	
end
